        <p>Unlike traditional RunFlat tires, the Dynamic RunFlat System allows for extended mobility, enabling drivers to safely continue their journey for a considerable distance after a puncture or air loss. This extended mobility can be crucial in remote or isolated areas, where access to immediate roadside assistance may be limited.</p>

        <h3>4. Compatibility and Integration:</h3>
        <p>The Dynamic RunFlat System is engineered to seamlessly integrate with a wide range of vehicle models, ensuring compatibility and ease of installation. This flexibility allows for widespread adoption and the potential to become a new industry standard.</p>

